k\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104epe1665702596013.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/epe1665702596013.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/epe1665702596013.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"epe1665702596013\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $interactive\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"epe1665702596013___interactive_270662\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return a boolean value indicating whether the current Form component is in interactive state.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"epe1665702596013__topic_d84899e1_d84900e1_d84901e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"epe1665702596013__p_d84902e1_d84903e1_d84904e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$interactive</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"epe1665702596013__topic_d56302e1_d56303e1_d56304e1_d56305e1_d56306e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1137119e66\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"epe1665702596013__table_d8873e1_d8874e1_d8875e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in $interactive</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"epe1665702596013__table_d8873e1_d8874e1_d8875e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"epe1665702596013__table_d8873e1_d8874e1_d8875e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"epe1665702596013__table_d8873e1_d8874e1_d8875e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"epe1665702596013__table_d8873e1_d8874e1_d8875e1__entry__2\">\n Form component is not in an interactive state.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"epe1665702596013__table_d8873e1_d8874e1_d8875e1__entry__1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"epe1665702596013__table_d8873e1_d8874e1_d8875e1__entry__2\">\n Form component is in an interactive state.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"epe1665702596013__table_d8873e1_d8874e1_d8875e1__entry__1\">\n 2\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"epe1665702596013__table_d8873e1_d8874e1_d8875e1__entry__2\">\n User interface of the form component is starting (an <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit/deferred</span> statement has just been executed).\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"epe1665702596013__topic_d56307e1_d56308e1_d56309e1_d56310e1_d56311e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1137119e130\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"epe1665702596013__d5909e20\">Use in Form components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"epe1665702596013__topic_d56312e1_d56313e1_d56314e1_d56315e1_d56316e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1137119e139\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"epe1665702596013__p_d84917e1_d84918e1_d84919e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$interactive</span> function allows you to test whether the current form component is in interactive state. Interactive state is started with either <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit/modal</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit/nonmodal</span>. It is terminated by executing either the accept or quit trigger.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"epe1665702596013__section_iwt_4p1_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1137119e158\">Example: Starting an Edit session if Application is not in Interactive Mode</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows how to start an edit session only if the\n               application is not already in interactive mode:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"epe1665702596013__pre_ows_pp1_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation editCustomer\n;- do an edit only if not already in interactive mode -\nif ( !$interactive )\n edit/nonmodal\nendif\nend\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gwk1665702595783.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>edit</a><p>Display the component in preparation for user input.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iqk1665702595933.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$editmode</a><p>Return or set a value that determines the degree to which a user can change data on the form component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527244\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527244\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$interactive Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $interactive Return a boolean value indicating whether the current Form component is in interactive state. $interactive Return Values Table 1. Values returned in $interactive Value Meaning 0 Form component is not in an interactive state. 1 Form component is in an interactive state. 2 User interface of the form component is starting (an edit/deferred statement has just been executed). Use Use in Form components. Description The $interactive function allows you to test whether the current form component is in interactive state. Interactive state is started with either edit/modal or edit/nonmodal . It is terminated by executing either the accept or quit trigger. Example: Starting an Edit session if Application is not in Interactive Mode The following example shows how to start an edit session only if the application is not already in interactive mode: operation editCustomer ;- do an edit only if not already in interactive mode - if ( !$interactive ) edit/nonmodal endif end Copy Related Links edit Display the component in preparation for user input. $editmode Return or set a value that determines the degree to which a user can change data on the form component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}